snippet.title: Multiplayer Gameplay Trailer  - Urban Warriors - Early Access
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2853810/Urban_Warriors/
Early Access available March 15th, 2024

4--Player Multiplayer Coop Adventure Mode & Versus Mode 3D Arena Fighter
indie game inspired by Power Stone, Dynamite Cop, Fighting Force, & Marvel Nemesis

Chaotix Game Development https://chaotix.games/
I love beat'em ups & arena fighters and hope you do too! Check out my in-development passion-project, a frantic 4 player arena fighting game featuring both versus & co-op adventure modes!


Stock Media provided by Spellrise / Pond5
